  "steps": [
    "Rinse all items with MilliQ before placing in dishwasher",
    "Use appropriate dishwashing rack for items. Make sure black hub is lined up in dishwasher",
    "Add a scoop of dishwashing detergent from white bucket under sink to detergent tray and close tray",
    "Close dishwasher door securely. Turn dial to appropriate wash cycle and press start."
